  "original_title": "\u0b9e\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0b95\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bcd  26 \u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The case against Gnanasara Thera has been adjourned till August 26",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The case against Gnanasara Thera's comment that Islam is a cancer has been adjourned to August 26.",
        "Today (01) witness hearings in the case on Friday and the request put forward by Gnanasara Thera for a public apology in the case were to be considered.",
        "In view of the current situation in the country, the case has been adjourned till August 26 without being taken up for hearing as per the circular issued by the Judicial Services Commission on the 27th.",
        "A case has been registered against Gnanasara Thera before the Additional Judge (Chamber No. 3) at the Colombo Chief Magistrate's Court in response to a complaint lodged by Rigas Hajiar, a member of the Board of Trustees of Boralai Zum Aa Church in the Colombo Crime Prevention Division.",
        "Witness hearings in the case began on June 8. Accordingly the first witness of the plaintiff has testified in court.",
        "In such a situation, Gnanasara Thera's lawyers have informed the court that his client is ready to apologize publicly in court with a view to concluding the case smoothly.",
        "It is noteworthy that the case was scheduled to be heard again on July 1."
      ],
